data.description: DIAMOND IN THE ROUGH! * Spacious 4 bed/3 full bath pool home with "good bones" is ready for a visionary investor! After giving the house and pool some overdue TLC, it can provide years of family reunions or rental income. Home is located in a refreshingly quiet community, yet only 30 minutes to all the exciting action at Disney! Cash or conventional only.
